snippet.textDisplay: Regarding comments saying to end the Pro Bowl: While the Pro Bowl aint much to watch, I suggest ending the game itself but still naming a roster. Players who have strong seasons deserve to have those seasons acknowledged and only 1 player can be MVP, only 1 player can be offensive player of the year and only one player can be defensive player of the year. So maybe get rid of the game itself, but still name a Pro Bowl roster so that the best players at every position each year can still get recognized.
